      <title>以色列议会支持反对巴勒斯坦建国的决议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-s-parliament-backs-resolution-opposing-palestinian-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列议会通过决议，正式反对建立独立的巴勒斯坦国，并警告称巴勒斯坦国可能成为恐怖组织的基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/israel-s-parliament-backs-resolution-opposing-palestinian-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国称银行必须改善对政治公众人物的待遇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-says-banks-must-improve-treatment-of-the-politically-exposed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国金融监管机构要求银行和其他贷方采取更多措施，确保议员、高级公务员及其家人不会受到不公平对待，因为人们担心一些客户会因为政治观点而被拒绝开立账户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/uk-says-banks-must-improve-treatment-of-the-politically-exposed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
