    <item>
      <title>中国誓言将推动高质量发展作为“首要任务”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/china-vows-to-push-for-high-quality-development-as-top-mission</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国家主席习近平承诺要让高质量发展成为世界第二大经济体的指导力量，并制定了推动中国在应对国内经济放缓和中美贸易紧张局势的同时向前发展的长期愿景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/china-vows-to-push-for-high-quality-development-as-top-mission</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告发现欧盟凝聚基金需要进行根本性改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/eu-cohesion-funds-need-a-fundamental-revamp-report-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲经济研究中心的报告显示，欧盟用来消除 27 个成员国中较贫穷和较富裕地区之间差异的 3920 亿欧元工具需要进行彻底改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/eu-cohesion-funds-need-a-fundamental-revamp-report-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:13:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业配额抗议活动蔓延 孟加拉国面临停摆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-faces-nationwide-shutdown-as-jobs-protest-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在示威活动演变为暴力事件后，学生抗议者向总理谢赫·哈西娜施压，要求废除政府的就业配额制度，孟加拉国将从周四开始关闭交通网络和企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-faces-nationwide-shutdown-as-jobs-protest-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:14:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙临时政府已准备好长期执政法国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/macron-s-caretaker-government-is-digging-in-for-the-long-haul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙正在为在未来数月内以权力有限的看守政府来管理法国做准备，因为他将把法国推向未知的宪法领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/macron-s-caretaker-government-is-digging-in-for-the-long-haul</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
